1. *Odbor za odbranu* zemlje je dao izjavu za javnost. (Committee for defense of the country made a statement to the public.)
2. Ministar odbrane je najavio povećanje vojnog budžeta. (*Ministar odbrane* - Minister of Defense announced an increase in the military budget.)
3. Vojska je uspešno *odbranila* grad od napada neprijatelja. (The army successfully *defended* the city from enemy attack.)
4. *Obrana* je bila veoma jaka i nisu uspeli da probiju naše redove. (*Defense* was very strong and they didn't manage to break through our lines.)
5. Džon je igrao u odbrani na utakmici. (John played in the *defense* during the game.)
6. Advokat je uspeo da *odbrani* svog klijenta i oslobodi ga optužbi. (The lawyer managed to *defend* his client and clear him of charges.)
7. *Odbornici* su raspravljali o tome kako poboljšati sistem odbrane grada. (*Councilors* discussed how to improve the city's defense system.)
8. Naš tim je odlično *odbranio* titulu šampiona. (Our team successfully *defended* the champion title.)